column5: Have you fished Sen Bay, if so, how was it? I camp near Sioux Lookout and fish mainly the Lost Lake area from Webster Bay to Decption Light. My group is considering trailering our boats to the Sen Bay area to try and fish further north. Do you know of any boat launches in that area? How far (time wise) is Sen Bay from Sioux Lookout (20, 30, 40 minutes)? Thanks!

Sen Bay is 30 minutes from Sioux Lookout max. I know of one launch, not a posted launch but you can launch a boat there. Send me an email at [email protected] and I will steer you in the right direction.
Just sent you an e-mail, thanks!
